{"lastModified":1774616688804,"uri":"c::18231584005::vessel::aba39dc0-a4e8-11f0-acf4-af4708853852","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\nWinter 2026/27: Red Sea (El Gouna)\n\nUnveil the exquisite Alina a Fountaine Pajot power 80 catamaran designed to charm and delight up to 10 guests in 5 lavish cabins, accompanied by a crew of 5 members. As the crowning jewel in Fountaine Pajot’s esteemed motor yacht collection, Alina embodies unparalleled elegance and sophistication. Crafted with extended cruising in mind, Alina offers a living space of unparalleled grandeur and vast outdoor areas ready for exploration. Renowned for its exceptional design, luxurious materials, and cutting-edge technology, Alina stands as a masterpiece at sea. Prepare to be captivated by her captivating aft cockpit, featuring multiple seating areas, and her opulent foredeck complete with a deck jacuzzi, sunbathing lounges, and a convenient wet bar for sun-soaked relaxation in style. Ascend to her expansive flybridge, where a dining table awaits for unforgettable ‘al fresco’ dining experiences with panoramic ocean views. Indoors, the main saloon beckons with a chic galley up layout perfect for interactive culinary experiences with a top-tier chef. Indulge in the luxuriously appointed cabins, including a magnificent owner’s suite and five gracious guest accommodations. Alina by Fountaine Pajot encapsulates opulence and adaptability, offering a sublime fusion of luxury, performance, and space to delight discerning clients in search of a truly extraordinary and memorable cruising experience. This is not just a voyage; it’s a grand adventure awaiting your embarkation.","blueprint":{"name":"ALINA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::aba39dc0-a4e8-11f0-acf4-af4708853852::assets::9cfdfcd0-a4f1-11f0-b024-3f1d7df60d3e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aba39dc0-a4e8-11f0-acf4-af4708853852::assets::9cfc0100-a4f1-11f0-b023-3f1d7df60d3e/{imageVariant